<span id="freeTextContainer7930095825300330736">To all the people that watched my brave struggle with this book; I dedicate this review to you.<br/>I have really mixed feelings about this one. Was it an absolute struggle to read? Did I fall asleep after a page or two many times? Was I wishing I was reading something else, something were things actually happened, like, I don&apos;t know say <a href='https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/6611315.The_Dark_Desires_Of_the_Druids_III_Desert_and_Destiny' title='The Dark Desires Of the Druids III Desert and Destiny by Isabel Roman' rel='nofollow noopener'>The Dark Desires Of the Druids III: Desert and Destiny</a>? The answer to all these questions is yes.<br/><br/>Now, was I reading it with a pencil in my hand underlining sentences</span>
